5A1F4B4A.Line1.6D03F: (sigh) Perhaps you are too young. The Prime Evils, you should know. Diablo, Mephisto, and Baal.

F413C4CC.Line3.6D03F: The Lessers are their rotten kin. Azmodan, Belial, Andariel, and Duriel. Each of them has ravaged humankind since the dawn of history, and they will gladly do so again.
